Newhaven Harbour Station

Newhaven Harbour Station is located within the county of East Sussex in South East England and is roughly 3.50 metres above sea-level.

The train station is situated on the Seaford Branch Line and falls inside the area governed by Lewes District Council.

Newhaven Harbour Station is operated by Unmapped (was Southern) and is unstaffed.
